    parentName: "ol"
  }, "This does not mean that all the effort is \u2018free\u2019, or that it is a project that supports \u2018digital slavery\u2019 (not paying people for their work); it is desirable to ensure the business model is defined in such a way that provides payment for peoples work; once everyone is paid, then perhaps the licensing conditions change on the outcomes.  "), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ol"
